# MuseDAM Master Workflow (Highest Priority)

## Trigger Conditions
- Any request involving Figma link, v0 link, design reskin, new component, color change, or UI implementation.

## Mandatory Execution Order (AI must follow exactly)
1. Read and enforce 05-musedam-globals-css.mdc (force-update if missing or outdated).
2. Check existing components via 01-musedam-core.mdc directory structure (reuse first).
3. Handle icons via 03-musedam-icons.mdc (Figma MCP → lucide-react).
4. Apply naming via 06-musedam-figma-layer-naming.mdc or v0 component name.
5. Execute reskin via 02-musedam-figma-make-reskin.mdc (Figma or v0 branch).
6. Validate with 04-musedam-tailwind.mdc (only CSS variables, gap only, no margin, correct radius).
7. Final check: 100% token usage, responsive, dark mode ready, data-component annotations.

Before any code output, explicitly state: “Following MuseDAM Master Workflow – globals.css enforced, components reused, icons synced.”